T01TD1133E:81b-1: aashta ma h'a sth'a na tsee tya sto tra /
T01TD1133E:81b-3: gnas chen po brgyad kyi mchod rten la bstod pa /
T01TD1133E:81b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:81b-5: 'gro ba'i bla ma gcig pu lumb'ir bltams //
T01TD1133E:81b-6: ser skya'i grong khyer gzhi ru gnas par mdzad //
T01TD1133E:81b-7: yon tan rin chen bye bas brgyan pa yi //
T01TD1133E:81b-8: bde gshegs mchod rten rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:81b-9: ma ga dh'a yi byang chub shing drung du //
T01TD1133E:81b-10: chu bo nee ranydza na zhes bya ba'i //
T01TD1133E:81b-11: 'gram bzhugs mchod rten yon tan rgya che ba //
T01TD1133E:81b-12: byang chub rten du gyur la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:81b-13: ka shi ka yi b'a r'a na s'i ru //
T01TD1133E:81b-14: chos kyi 'khor lo rnam grol rmad byung ni //
T01TD1133E:81b-15: nyon mongs sgrib pa rnam par gcod mdzad pa //
T01TD1133E:81b-16: ye shes mchod rten bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:81b-17: mnyan du yod par gzhan stobs tshar bcad nas //
T01TD1133E:81b-18: dze ta'i tshal du cho 'phrul chen po bstan //
T01TD1133E:81b-19: sa gsum dgongs pa mchog tu bsgrub mdzad pa //
T01TD1133E:81b-20: mu stegs pham mdzad mchod rten phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:81b-21: grong khyer dam pa mchog ni gsal ldan du //
T01TD1133E:81b-22: lha rnams gnas gshegs bla na med par babs //
T01TD1133E:81b-23: zhabs la tshangs dbang cod pan gyis mchod pa //
T01TD1133E:81b-24: sum cu'i lhas mchod mchod rten phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:81b-25: dge 'dun dbyen du sngar gyur las //
T01TD1133E:81b-26: ston pa'i nyan thos rab mthun pa //
T01TD1133E:81b-27: rgyal po'i khab kyi 'od ma'i tshal //
T01TD1133E:81b-28: byams nges mchod rten phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:81b-29: sku tshe 'du byed btang ba las //
T01TD1133E:81b-30: slar yang sku tshe byin brlabs pa //
T01TD1133E:81b-31: rnam grol yangs pa can gyi ni //
T01TD1133E:81b-32: byin rlabs mchod rten phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1133E:82a-2: / dge ba la ni sbyor mdzad cing //
T01TD1133E:82a-3: 'gran med gyad gnas zung gi tshal //
T01TD1133E:82a-5: sh'akya thub mchod rten brgyad po dag / phyogs bcu gzhan dang gzhan rnams na //
T01TD1133E:82a-6: bzhugs pa'i chos sku kun la 'dud //
T01TD1133E:82a-7: zhi la rtag tu spyis phyag 'tshal ;
T01TD1133E:82a-8: /'di ltar spros pa kun bral dpe med rtag cing dag pa'i ngo bo nyid //
T01TD1133E:82a-9: sangs rgyas chos sku mkha' ltar 'gro ba la khyab yang dag phyag 'tshal bas //
T01TD1133E:82a-10: bsod nams gangs ri'i kha dog ltar dkar bdag gi rgyud la gang bsags pa //
T01TD1133E:82a-11: des ni sems can ma lus ting 'dzin bde rtogs byang chub thob par shog / gnas chen po brgyad kyi mchod rten la bstod pa /
T01TD1133E:82a-12: slob dpon chen po 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
